@startuml Sequence_Auth
!theme blueprint
title URL Shortener — JWT Authentication Sequence

skinparam sequenceArrowColor #6366f1
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #f0f4ff

actor "User" as USER
participant "React\nFrontend" as REACT
participant "AuthController" as CTRL
participant "AuthService" as SVC
participant "JwtService" as JWT
participant "MySQL" as DB
participant "BCrypt" as BC

== Registration Flow ==

USER -> REACT : fill register form\n(name, email, password)
REACT -> CTRL : POST /api/auth/register
CTRL -> SVC : register(request)
SVC -> DB : existsByEmail(email)?
DB --> SVC : false (new user)
SVC -> BC : encode(plainPassword)
BC --> SVC : "$2a$10$hashedPassword..."
SVC -> DB : save(User entity)
DB --> SVC : saved user
SVC -> JWT : generateToken(userDetails)
JWT --> SVC : "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..."
SVC --> CTRL : AuthResponse{token, email, name}
CTRL --> REACT : 200 OK + JWT token
REACT -> REACT : localStorage.setItem('token', jwt)
REACT --> USER : logged in — navbar shows name

== Login Flow ==

USER -> REACT : fill login form
REACT -> CTRL : POST /api/auth/login
CTRL -> SVC : login(request)
SVC -> DB : findByEmail(email)
DB --> SVC : User entity
SVC -> BC : matches(plain, hashed)?
BC --> SVC : true
SVC -> JWT : generateToken(userDetails)
JWT --> SVC : new JWT token (24h expiry)
SVC --> CTRL : AuthResponse{token, email, name}
CTRL --> REACT : 200 OK + JWT token
REACT --> USER : logged in

== Protected Request Flow (Dashboard) ==

USER -> REACT : click Dashboard
REACT -> REACT : read token from localStorage
REACT -> CTRL : GET /api/my-urls\nAuthorization: Bearer eyJ...

note over CTRL
    JwtAuthFilter intercepts
    every request automatically
end note

CTRL -> JWT : extractUsername(token)
JWT --> CTRL : "user@email.com"
CTRL -> DB : loadUserByUsername(email)
DB --> CTRL : UserDetails
CTRL -> JWT : isTokenValid(token, userDetails)
JWT --> CTRL : true
CTRL -> CTRL : set SecurityContext authentication

CTRL --> REACT : 200 OK + user's URLs list
REACT --> USER : dashboard table

== Token Expired ==

REACT -> CTRL : GET /api/my-urls\n(expired token)
CTRL -> JWT : isTokenValid → false
CTRL --> REACT : 401 Unauthorized
REACT -> REACT : clear localStorage\nredirect to login
REACT --> USER : login page

@enduml
